      <br><strong>5-Ton Lorry:</strong> RM300-RM500 annually
      <br><strong>10-Ton Lorry:</strong> RM400-RM600 annually
      <br><strong>Prime Mover:</strong> RM500-RM800 annually</p>

      <h2>Consequences of Operating Without APAD Permit</h2>

      <h3>Legal Penalties</h3>

      <p><strong>First Offense:</strong>
      <br>• Compound fine: RM500-RM2,000
      <br>• Lorry impoundment: Until permit obtained
      <br>• Court appearance required (certain cases)</p>

      <p><strong>Repeat Offense:</strong>
      <br>• Compound fine: RM2,000-RM5,000
      <br>• Lorry impoundment: Extended period
      <br>• Business license suspension risk</p>

      <h3>Business Impact</h3>

      <p><strong>Immediate Consequences:</strong>
      <br>• Lorry impounded: Cannot operate
      <br>• Client commitments: Cannot fulfill
      <br>• Revenue lost: RM1,500-RM3,000 daily</p>

